0:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3694:\"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/wp-gutenberg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-731\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/wp-gutenberg.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/wp-gutenberg-300x150.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/wpvi-5.0-blue.svg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Gutenberg  chnh thc pht hnh cng phin bn WordPress 5.0 vo ngy 06/12/2018. Sau y l nhng im ng lu  ca phin bn c ci tin ng k ny.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-727\"></span>\n\n\n\n<h2>Xy dng ni dung a dng hn vi &#8220;Block&#8221;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Gutenberg cung cp tri nghim v &#8220;block&#8221; (khi) r rng hn v mt b cc. Thay v mt ni dung trn cng, nay bn  c th chia ct, thm media, thm cc tu bin ni dung mi cho bi vit phong ph hn, bao gm c &#8220;th&#8221;. Mi loi ni dung bn thn s l mt &#8220;block&#8221;.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Danh sch cc khi  h tr</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/wordpress-gutenberg-blocks.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-730\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/wordpress-gutenberg-blocks.png 702w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/wordpress-gutenberg-blocks-300x288.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngoi nhng block cung cp sn, tnh nng &#8220;Block ti s dng&#8221; cng  c mt, cho php bn to cc khi tu bin ring ca mnh v ti s dng n ti cc trang khc d dng.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Giao din mi Twenty Nineteen</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Giao din do nhm Core pht trin nhm pht huy tt c sc mnh ca Gutenberg. Trng d nhn, b cc ti gin nhng khng km phn hin i.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/twenty-nineteen.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-729\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/twenty-nineteen.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/12/twenty-nineteen-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nu bn quan tm v mun tham gia dch giao din ny, hy lm <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Nu bn quan tm v mun tham gia dch giao din ny, hy lm ti y nh.   (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/vi/default/wp-themes/twentynineteen\" target=\"_blank\">ti y</a> nh.  </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Bn cha sn sng s dng Gutenberg?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hy ti <a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/plugins/classic-editor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Hy ti plugin Classic Editor v v ci vo, Gutenberg s khng cn hot ng trn website ca bn na nh.\n (opens in a new tab)\">plugin Classic Editor</a> v v ci vo, Gutenberg s khng cn hot ng trn website ca bn na nh.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cc ti liu tham kho dnh cho Gutenberg<br></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dnh cho lp trnh vin: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Dnh cho lp trnh vin: Gutenberg Handbook\n (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/gutenberg/handbook/\" target=\"_blank\">Gutenberg Handbook</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Ngun: </em><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Ngun: WPHub (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://wphub.vn/wordpress50/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>WPHub</em></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2018/12/07/wordpress-5-0-bebo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"\n		\