(327, 102, 'new_right_content', '<h1 class=\"title-page\">NOVAWORLD PHAN THIET PHT TRIN THEO M HNH I  TH DU LCH NGH DNG GII TR</h1>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix mrb20\">\r\n\r\nTheo n v pht trin, d n tch hp a dng tin ch ng cp quc t nhm tn dng tim nng bt ng sn du lch ti Phan Thit.\r\n\r\n<strong>Li th v tr ven bin</strong>\r\n\r\nTheo s liu t S Vn ha, Th thao v Du lch tnh, trong qu I/2019, Bnh Thun n khong 1,53 triu lt khch du lch, trong , khch quc t khong 199.252 lt, tng 15% so vi cng k 2018.\r\n\r\nTim nng t bin ng gp khng nh vo s pht trin du lch, ng thi  thc y bt ng sn ngh dng ti y. Vi li th ng b bin di gn 58 km, nhiu bi ct trng, cnh quan nguyn s v kh hu m p quanh nm, Phan Thit c tnh Bnh Thun nh hng pht trin thnh t hp  th du lch bin trong tng lai.\r\n\r\nTrong cc d n ngh dng ang pht trin ti y, i  th du lch ngh dng gii tr NovaWorld Phan Thiet vi quy m gn 1.000ha c nhiu c im ni tri, cng a dng cc sn phm  u t nh grand villa, villa, mini villa, townhouse, shophouse... tm nhn hng ra khung cnh bin.\r\n\r\n</div>'),
