(353, 110, 'new_left_content', '<h1 class=\"title-page\">NOVAWORLD PHAN THIET PHT TRIN THEO M HNH I  TH DU LCH NGH DNG GII TR</h1>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix mrb20\">\r\n\r\nTheo n v pht trin, d n tch hp a dng tin ch ng cp quc t nhm tn dng tim nng bt ng sn du lch ti Phan Thit.\r\n\r\n<strong>Li th v tr ven bin</strong>\r\n\r\nTheo s liu t S Vn ha, Th thao v Du lch tnh, trong qu I/2019, Bnh Thun n khong 1,53 triu lt khch du lch, trong , khch quc t khong 199.252 lt, tng 15% so vi cng k 2018.\r\n\r\nTim nng t bin ng gp khng nh vo s pht trin du lch, ng thi  thc y bt ng sn ngh dng ti y. Vi li th ng b bin di gn 58 km, nhiu bi ct trng, cnh quan nguyn s v kh hu m p quanh nm, Phan Thit c tnh Bnh Thun nh hng pht trin thnh t hp  th du lch bin trong tng lai.\r\n\r\nTrong cc d n ngh dng ang pht trin ti y, i  th du lch ngh dng gii tr NovaWorld Phan Thiet vi quy m gn 1.000ha c nhiu c im ni tri, cng a dng cc sn phm  u t nh grand villa, villa, mini villa, townhouse, shophouse... tm nhn hng ra khung cnh bin.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.novaland.com.vn/Data/Sites/1/media/tin-tuc/2019/VNE1.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<em>NovaWorld Phan Thiet a dng loi sn phm second home vi tm nhn hng ra khung cnh bin.\r\n</em>\r\n\r\nThm vo , d n s hu v tr thun li khi tha hng h tng giao thng hon thin nh ng cao tc TP HCM - Long Thnh - Du Giy - Phan Thit hon thnh vo nm 2021, cao tc Nha Trang - Vnh Ho d kin khi cng nm 2019, tu ha 5 sao, cng bin cho tu du lch vi sc cha 3.000-5.000 du khch, sn bay Phan Thit vi tng vn u t 10.000 t ng...\r\n\r\nH thng h tng ny s gip rt ngn khong cch t cc tnh thnh khc v Phan Thit v to thm sc nng cho th trng ngh dng ti y.\r\n\r\n<strong>M hnh i  th du lch ngh dng gii tr</strong>\r\n\r\nD n NovaWorld Phan Thiet c xy dng theo m hnh i  th du lch ngh dng gii tr \"tt c trong mt\" ang c a chung hin nay, nhm p ng ti a nhu cu ca du khch.\r\n\r\n\"Chng ti k vng pht trin NovaWorld Phan Thiet thnh mt \'im n tuyt ho\'  ngh ngi, th gin ca cc gia nh v du khch quc t\", i din tp on Novaland chia s.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.novaland.com.vn/Data/Sites/1/media/tin-tuc/2019/vvn2.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<em>NovaWorld Phan Thiet c ch u t k vng tr thnh \"im n tuyt ho\" ti \"vng t ha\" Phan Thit.\r\n</em>\r\n\r\nBn cnh cc t hp lu tr vi kin trc c trng t nhiu quc gia trn th gii, NovaWorld Phan Thiet s xy dng cm tin ch ng cp quc t ln u tin ti khu vc Phan Thit nh: trung tm th thao phc hp khong 220ha bao gm cm sn golf 36 l theo tiu chun quc t  iu kin  ng k t chc gii PGA Tour (Hi golf th chuyn nghip), khu thi u th thao trong nh, ngoi tri, sn vn ng, cm cng vin ch , cng vin nc; cng vin thiu nhi.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, cn c khu phc hp trung tm thng mi - hi ngh - m thc - gii tr cho gia nh; lot khch sn 3-5 sao, khch sn Boutique; khu resort, International Clinic - spa (trung tm chm sc sc khe, thm m quc t)...\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.novaland.com.vn/Data/Sites/1/media/tin-tuc/2019/vvn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<em>D n hon thnh s c cc cu lc b th thao bin vi nhiu tr chi mo him.\r\n</em>\r\n\r\nTn dng a th gip 7km mt bin, NovaWorld Phan Thiet s pht trin m hnh cng vin bi bin (bikini beach) quy m khong 16ha; gm nhiu tin ch c o nh Ocean Lagoon( bi bin chn sng), qung trng sn khu ngoi tri theo kin trc Colosseum, bar, khu mua sm ven bin... cng nhng hot ng th thao mo him nh lt vn bay, trt nc...\r\n\r\nChui tin ch v th dc th thao ti NovaWorld Phan Thiet c k vng gp phn a ni y tr thnh trung tm ngh dng gii tr, th thao bin ca khu vc chu .\r\n\r\nng ch  vi chiu di 2km, hng mc \"con ng di sn\" nm gia lng i  th du lch ngh dng gii tr NovaWorld Phan Thiet s l ni hi t tinh hoa m thc cng cc l hi, cc bui trnh din ngh thut truyn thng, v khu ch nng sn ln t cc tnh Khnh Ha, Bnh Thun, Lm ng...\r\n\r\n</div>'),
