s.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://www.novaland.com.vn/Data/Sites/1/media/tin-tuc/2019/vvn2.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<em>NovaWorld Phan Thiet c ch u t k vng tr thnh \"im n tuyt ho\" ti \"vng t ha\" Phan Thit.\r\n</em>\r\n\r\nBn cnh cc t hp lu tr vi kin trc c trng t nhiu quc gia trn th gii, NovaWorld Phan Thiet s xy dng cm tin ch ng cp quc t ln u tin ti khu vc Phan Thit nh: trung tm th thao phc hp khong 220ha bao gm cm sn golf 36 l theo tiu chun quc t  iu kin  ng k t chc gii PGA Tour (Hi golf th chuyn nghip), khu thi u th thao trong nh, ngoi tri, sn vn ng, cm cng vin ch , cng vin nc; cng vin thiu nhi.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, cn c khu phc hp trung tm thng mi - hi ngh - m thc - gii tr cho gia nh; lot khch sn 3-5 sao, khch sn Boutique; khu resort, International Clinic - spa (trung tm chm sc sc khe, thm m quc t)...\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://www.novaland.com.vn/Data/Sites/1/media/tin-tuc/2019/vvn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<em>D n hon thnh s c cc cu lc b th thao bin vi nhiu tr chi mo him.\r\n</em>\r\n\r\nTn dng a th gip 7km mt bin, NovaWorld Phan Thiet s pht trin m hnh cng vin bi bin (bikini beach) quy m khong 16ha; gm nhiu tin ch c o nh Ocean Lagoon( bi bin chn sng), qung trng sn khu ngoi tri theo kin trc Colosseum, bar, khu mua sm ven bin... cng nhng hot ng th thao mo him nh lt vn bay, trt nc...\r\n\r\nChui tin ch v th dc th thao ti NovaWorld Phan Thiet c k vng gp phn a ni y tr thnh trung tm ngh dng gii tr, th thao bin ca khu vc chu .\r\n\r\nng ch  vi chiu di 2km, hng mc \"con ng di sn\" nm gia lng i  th du lch ngh dng gii tr NovaWorld Phan Thiet s l ni hi t tinh hoa m thc cng cc l hi, cc bui trnh din ngh thut truyn thng, v khu ch nng sn ln t cc tnh Khnh Ha, Bnh Thun, Lm ng...\r\n\r\n</div>'),
