(132, 1, '2019-06-05 13:40:17', '2019-06-05 13:40:17', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Cu hi t ra l cc nh u t nn bt u nh th no?</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trc tin cc nh u t phi tm hiu v phn tch nhu cu khch hng ban u v ng thi tm hiu v cc d n t nn ti cc khu vc  th v la chn cho mnh nhng mnh t c gi tr v ph hp  xy dng nh ngh. Khu vc c Ha hin nay ang l ni c nhiu khch hng quan tm v  x v ni ny  xy dng v u t vi li th ni tri mt  dn s v cc cm Khu Cng Nghip bao quanh hng trm ngn cng nhn sinh sng v lm vic t cc tnh thnh nn y l ngun lc quan trng  kim 1 ming t u t cho vic xy nh ngh khch sn thu ht lng khch rt ng mi ngyTrong  d n An Phc Center 5 l 1 trong nhng d n t nn khan him nm ngay trung tm th trn l d n khan him trn th trng c mt  dn c hin hu t ODT (  th) ng  khch hng quan tm v chn  l ni  u t sinh li.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Kh nng ri ro thp.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nh ngh c nhiu nh u t nhn nh l hnh thc kinh doanh khng ho th pht bi li th u t ngn hn, li nhun lu di m ri ro gn nh bng khng. V vy, vic tm kim ngun khch hng d dng hn bao gi ht. Vi tnh hnh cung khng  cu ca cc nh ngh vo nhng t cao im, cc ch u t khng cn lo lng n vic b trng phng. D vo t thp im nht th s lng khch vn c th duy tr v m bo ngun thu.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1254,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-PHAN-LO-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-HOAN-CHINH-NGAY-03-11-2018-png-01.png?x86971\"><img src=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-PHAN-LO-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-HOAN-CHINH-NGAY-03-11-2018-png-01-1024x783.png?x86971\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1254\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>u t t nn trung tm xy dng qun c ph sn vn.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kin