(164, 1, '2019-06-07 14:17:14', '2019-06-07 14:17:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>V tr vng</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Th trn c Ha c mt v tr v cng quan trng trong s nghip pht trin cng nghip v du lch sinh thi ca tnh Long An, vi cc khu cng nghip nh Tn , Hnh Phc , Tn c , c Ha I,II,III , Cm khu cng nghip Hong Gia, Xuyn .. v khu du lch Phc Lc Th Vi v tr l ca ng i vo TP.HCM, th trn c Ha c nhiu d n ln i qua a bn nh tuyn ng Vnh ai 4, Cng quc t.  l nhng li th h tng  c Ha pht trin cng nghip v dch v. Ngoi nm cnh cc khu cng nghip k trn d n ph tr An Phc vi y  cc tin ch xung quanh t trng hc , siu th , ch , khu gii tr cng l li th gip c Ha vng 1 tm cao</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":159,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/so-do-phan-lo-an-phuc-central-land-18_07_2018.jpg\"><img src=\"http://housing.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/so-do-phan-lo-an-phuc-central-land-18_07_2018-768x543.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-159\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Tin ch khi nm gn khu dn c hin hu</strong>Vi dn s gn 300.000 ngi ang tp trung sinh sng ti y, Th trn c Ha l khu vc c y  cc cng trnh cng cng hin hu c xy dng tng i c quy m v kin c nh: tr s Huyn U, Hi ng Nhn Dn v U Ban Nhn Dn ca huyn, Nh vn ha, Trng PTTH, Trng dy ngh, Bu in, Ngn hng, Ch, Khu dn c, Bnh vin a khoa, Th gii di ng , in My Xanh , in my Ch Ln, Viettel StoreRt thch hp pht trin cc ngnh dch v nh gio dc, y t, vn ha, th thao, thng mi, gii tr cng cng, ti chnh, ngn hng, bu in, du lch, vn ti,Th trn c Ha ang l tm im thu ht i a s dn c n y sinh sng v lm vic.<strong><a href=\"https://diaocanphuc.com.vn/an-phuc-central/\">An Phc CenTral</a>&nbsp;tha hng c cc li th t khu dn c hin hu</strong>An Phc Central c v tr v cng thun tin v giao thng khi cch Th Trn Bn Lc 20km , cch Tp. H Ch Minh 2km. Hn na, Ph Tr An Phc nm trong khu vc v cch d n trng im nh ng vnh ai 4 khong 2km.Xung quanh d n, y  cc tin ch hin hu nh: trng THPT Thng Nht A l trng im ca huyn, cc trng THPT t thc nh: THPT Trn i Ngha, THPT Trn Quc Tun, THPT Vn Lang; UBND huyn Trng Bom; Bnh vin a khoa Trng Bom; Trung tm TDTT; Khu thng mi dch v; Nh hng; Spa; Ngn hng,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":160,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/SO-DO-LIEN-KET-DO-THI-DUC-HOA.jpg\"><img src=\"http://housing.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SO-DO-LIEN-KET-DO-THI-DUC-HOA-768x543.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-160\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Khu  Th An Phc', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'khu-do-thi-an-phuc', '', '', '2019-06-07 14:19:26', '2019-06-07 14:19:26', '', 0, 'http://housing.test/?p=164', 0, 'post', '', 0),
