(245, 1, '2019-06-12 15:54:15', '2019-06-12 15:54:15', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1162,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bat-dong-san-thanh-pho.jpg?x86971\"><img src=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bat-dong-san-thanh-pho-300x172.jpg?x86971\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1162\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Trong lc cn h ang bo ho lm cho iu ng th phn khc t nn gi r xem ra l s la chn kh thi v khn ngoan nht cho nh u t.</strong>Vo thi im ny, khi cc sn vng  ng ca, ngun vn u t  vo th trng chng khon. Nhng sau th trng chng khon, ngun vn ca hng triu nh u t s  v u nu khng phi l th trng bt ng sn Cn Giuc, tnh Long An</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>y s l cc l do  cc nh u t vo bt ng sn&nbsp;<a href=\"https://diaocanphuc.com.vn/tai-sao-phai-mua-dat-can-giuoc-long-an/\">Cn Giuc, Long An:</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li><strong>Quy hoch ng b v quy m nht</strong></li><li><strong>C s h tng hon chnh v ng b nht</strong></li><li><strong>Thu ht vn u t nhanh v nhiu nht</strong></li><li><strong>Tc  xy dng d n ti Long An nhanh nht</strong></li><li><strong>Gi thnh bt ng sn ang cn r</strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cn Giuc, Long An c v tr lin k Thnh ph H Ch Minh vi tc  pht trin cc k nhanh vi tng mc vn u t nc ngoi lun nm trong top u ca c nc. Tc  pht trin nhanh GDP cao, thu ht vn mnh, vi h tng thng minh, chnh sch thng minh, mc tiu phn u ca Long An n nm 2020, tnh Long An c bn tr thnh tnh cng nghip. y l ni d dng  cc nh u t sinh li nhanh chng cng nh v lu di.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nm trong vng kinh t trng im pha Nam, Cn Giuc-&nbsp;Long An&nbsp;c nhng li th vt tri m khng mt ni&nbsp;no c c. Cn Giuc, Long An l mt trong s t nhng vng t hi t c&nbsp;<strong>3 yu t vng trong u t bt ng sn  l: Thin thi, a li, nhn ha.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo quy hoch vng mi trong tng lai, Cn Giuc c chia thnh 6 vng, trong  vng h s pht trin thnh vng cng nghip-  th v dch v. Trong thi gian ti, nhng con ng hon thnh s c nhng t ph mi, a kinh t vng h Cn Giuc pht trin, trong  kt ni Thnh ph H Ch Minh vi Cng quc t Long An, k c cng Hip Phc, Thnh ph H Ch Minh. Ngoi ra Cn Giuc cn kt ni giao thng ng Tn Tp- c Ha, y l mt trong nhng cng trnh ht sc quan trng  pht huy, khai thc hiu qu Cng quc t Long An. n lc , c th ni, Cn Giuc c bn xy dng nn tng cng nghip ti a phng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Nhng nn&nbsp;u t bt ng sn&nbsp;vo phn khc no  hiu qu cao nht??</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trn th trng c nhiu mc gi t nn c rao bn: t 99 triu- 600 triu/nn (tnh chung theo din tch 100m<sup>2</sup>).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong  mc gi t 99 triu-139 triu: Mt l, t s chung cha c s ring, hoc thanh ton nhiu t  ch u t c thi gian v tin ng tng t  tch s (nhng khng m bo thi gian c th  nhn s); Hai l, v tr khng p xa trung tm, khng gn cc tin ch kh c kh nng sinh li.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi mc gi 160 triu-350 triu/nn din tch 100m<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;ti&nbsp;cc khu Ti nh c,h tng hon thin theo tiu chun, &nbsp;s ring th c 100%, v tr p d dng sinh li ngay hoc u t lu di.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc gi t 350 triu-700 triu tr ln/nn: gi cao, mc vn b ra kh ln nhng hiu qu v kinh doanh hay  lin c bit mang li gi tr t bin cao.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C th khng nh , th trng&nbsp;<strong>BS Cn Giuc</strong>&nbsp;s lun dn u v  hp dn m kh c huyn no c th cnh tranh c, c bit y l ni pht trin bt ng sn dnh cho cc nh u t ti Long An.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'To sao phi mua t gn Cn Giuc Long An', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tao-sao-phai-mua-dat-gan-can-giuoc-long-an', '', '', '2019-06-12 15:54:19', '2019-06-12 15:54:19', '', 0, 'http://housing.test/?p=245', 0, 'post', '', 0),
