c&nbsp;<strong>3 yu t vng trong u t bt ng sn  l: Thin thi, a li, nhn ha.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo quy hoch vng mi trong tng lai, Cn Giuc c chia thnh 6 vng, trong  vng h s pht trin thnh vng cng nghip-  th v dch v. Trong thi gian ti, nhng con ng hon thnh s c nhng t ph mi, a kinh t vng h Cn Giuc pht trin, trong  kt ni Thnh ph H Ch Minh vi Cng quc t Long An, k c cng Hip Phc, Thnh ph H Ch Minh. Ngoi ra Cn Giuc cn kt ni giao thng ng Tn Tp- c Ha, y l mt trong nhng cng trnh ht sc quan trng  pht huy, khai thc hiu qu Cng quc t Long An. n lc , c th ni, Cn Giuc c bn xy dng nn tng cng nghip ti a phng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Nhng nn&nbsp;u t bt ng sn&nbsp;vo phn khc no  hiu qu cao nht??</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trn th trng c nhiu mc gi t nn c rao bn: t 99 triu- 600 triu/nn (tnh chung theo din tch 100m<sup>2</sup>).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong  mc gi t 99 triu-139 triu: Mt l, t s chung cha c s ring, hoc thanh ton nhiu t  ch u t c thi gian v tin ng tng t  tch s (nhng khng m bo thi gian c th  nhn s); Hai l, v tr khng p xa trung tm, khng gn cc tin ch kh c kh nng sinh li.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi mc gi 160 triu-350 triu/nn din tch 100m<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;ti&nbsp;cc khu Ti nh c,h tng hon thin theo tiu chun, &nbsp;s ring th c 100%, v tr p d dng sinh li ngay hoc u t lu di.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc gi t 350 triu-700 triu tr ln/nn: gi cao, mc vn b ra kh ln nhng hiu qu v kinh doanh hay  lin c bit mang li gi tr t bin cao.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C th khng nh , th trng&nbsp;<strong>BS Cn Giuc</strong>&nbsp;s lun dn u v  hp dn m kh c huyn no c th cnh tranh c, c bit y l ni pht trin bt ng sn dnh cho cc nh u t ti Long An.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'To sao phi mua t gn Cn Giuc Long An', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '245-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-12 15:54:15', '2019-06-12 15:54:15', '', 245, 'http://housing.test/?p=247', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
