(249, 1, '2019-06-12 16:34:40', '2019-06-12 16:34:40', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Cu hi t ra l cc nh u t nn bt u nh th no?</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trc tin cc nh u t phi tm hiu v phn tch nhu cu khch hng ban u v ng thi tm hiu v cc d n t nn ti cc khu vc  th v la chn cho mnh nhng mnh t c gi tr v ph hp  xy dng nh ngh. Khu vc c Ha hin nay ang l ni c nhiu khch hng quan tm v  x v ni ny  xy dng v u t vi li th ni tri mt  dn s v cc cm Khu Cng Nghip bao quanh hng trm ngn cng nhn sinh sng v lm vic t cc tnh thnh nn y l ngun lc quan trng  kim 1 ming t u t cho vic xy nh ngh khch sn thu ht lng khch rt ng mi ngyTrong  d n An Phc Center 5 l 1 trong nhng d n t nn khan him nm ngay trung tm th trn l d n khan him trn th trng c mt  dn c hin hu t ODT (  th) ng  khch hng quan tm v chn  l ni  u t sinh li.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Kh nng ri ro thp.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nh ngh c nhiu nh u t nhn nh l hnh thc kinh doanh khng ho th pht bi li th u t ngn hn, li nhun lu di m ri ro gn nh bng khng. V vy, vic tm kim ngun khch hng d dng hn bao gi ht. Vi tnh hnh cung khng  cu ca cc nh ngh vo nhng t cao im, cc ch u t khng cn lo lng n vic b trng phng. D vo t thp im nht th s lng khch vn c th duy tr v m bo ngun thu.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1254,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-PHAN-LO-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-HOAN-CHINH-NGAY-03-11-2018-png-01.png?x86971\"><img src=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-PHAN-LO-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-HOAN-CHINH-NGAY-03-11-2018-png-01-1024x783.png?x86971\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1254\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>u t t nn trung tm xy dng qun c ph sn vn.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kinh doanh c ph sn vn trong vi nm tr li y khng ngng pht trin v mang v nhng khon li nhun ln cho nh kinh doanh. Nhng qun c ph sn vn p ng  mi yu t nh thit k p, khng gian hi ha s cc k ht khch v em v mc li nhun bn vng mi ngy vi v tr t nn&nbsp;<a href=\"https://diaocanphuc.com.vn/khu-do-thi-thuong-mai-dich-vu-an-phuc-center-5/#more-1257\"><strong>Khu  Th -Thng Mi  Dch V Center 5</strong></a>&nbsp;p ng  yu cu khi khch hng la chn ni y  u t qun c ph sn vn .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi v tr c a khan him nm ngay trung tm th trn c ha ch cch cng vin V Vn Tn 200m xung quanh dn c hin hu vi hn 100 ngn cng nhn v sinh vin trng i Hc Quc T Tn To ang sinh sng v lm vic ti khu vc ny y c xem l iu kin thun li nht khi mt  dn c ng c rt thch hp cho vic u t bn vng c khon li nhun khng l bng vic xy dng qun c ph sn vn ti khu vc ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>5 l do nn chn Khu  Th  Thng Mi  Dch V An Phc Center 5 Kinh Doanh nh hng qun nhu.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>t nn Trung tm th trn.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>y c xem l l do u tin bi v tr d n t nn&nbsp;<strong>Khu  Th  Thng Mi  Dch V An Phc Center 5&nbsp;</strong>nm ngay trn mt tin TL825 vi l gii 60m i qua cc tnh thnh giao thng thun li vi mt  dn c lp y nhu cu sinh hot cc dch v n ung tng cao hn bao gi ht ti ni y  thu ht hng ngn lng cng nhn t cc tnh thnh v y lm vic v sinh sng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti Khu vc c ha vi khon u t bn vng li nhun tng cao tng ngy vi t nn gi r t trung tm ch 12 n 13 triu/m2 b ra mt khon u t t so vi thnh ph mt mt vung t ln c 100 triu khch hng mi c v tr tt  u t&nbsp; xy dng nh hng qun nhu nhng n vi t nn An Phc Center 5 vi v tr trung tm p ng ht cc yu t kinh doanh thch hp nht cho vic&nbsp; u t bn vng ti ni y.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1255,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-VI-TRI-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-A0-841-X-1189CM-png-01.png?x86971\"><img src=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-VI-TRI-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-A0-841-X-1189CM-png-01-1024x725.png?x86971\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1255\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Mt  dn c hin hu.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Khu  Th  Thng Mi  Dch V An Phc Center 5&nbsp;</strong>dn c hin hu xung quanh mt  dn c lp y l yu t quyt nh th trng kinh doanh bun bn  ni y vi nghnh ngh kinh doanh xy dng nh hng qun nhu ti khu vc ny rt t ch c mt vi qun c u t bi bn lng khch hng rt ng t cc khu cng nghip v cc chuyn gia&nbsp; lm vn phng thng chn qun sch s  n tra cm vn phng nn u t xy nh hng n ung ti ni y rt thch hp cho cc i tng ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Khon u t bn vng li nhun tng cao tng ngy.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi v tr t trung tm khu  th hin ti qu t khng cn nhiu cho vic p ng nhu cu m nh hng bun bn kinh doanh cc dch v nn nhiu i gia si gn  x v c ha mnh tay mua nhiu l t din tch ln  u t nh hng khch sn bi khon cch v giao thng thun li ch 25 pht v ti trung tm thnh ph vi gi t ti ni y ang cn rt r u t b vn t nhng doanh thu cao bng khu vc thnh ph chnh v th la chn t nn ti&nbsp;<strong>Khu  Th  Thng Mi  Dch V An Phc Center 5&nbsp;</strong>l la&nbsp; chn s 1 hp l nht cho nhu cu u t nh hng khch sn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1260,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":544,\"height\":768,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-VE-TINH-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-01.png?x86971\"><img src=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SO-DO-VE-TINH-AN-PHUC-CENTER-5-01-725x1024.png?x86971\" alt=\"An Phc CENTER 5\" class=\"wp-image-1260\" width=\"544\" height=\"768\"/></a><figcaption>An Phc CENTER 5</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Lin k cc cm khu cng nghip ln.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khu vc c Ha ang l khu vc th trn nhn nhp v m bi hng trm ngn cng nhn t cc x nghip ln ko theo nhu cu n ung  tr cc dch v bun bn tp np hng ngy mt  dn c ng c dn ti vic khch hng mnh dn u t  kinh doanh nh hng khch sn l iu ng nhin vi v tr t c a khan him trung tm th trn&nbsp;<strong>Khu  Th  Thng Mi  Dch V An Phc Center 5&nbsp;</strong>rt thch hp cho qu khch hng mua t 3 nn tr ln  thun li cho vic u t sinh li bn vng ti ni y.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Giao thng thun li.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Giao thng thun li c xem xem l yu t quyt nh khi m nh hng qun nhu ti v tr d n&nbsp;<strong>Khu  Th  Thng Mi  Dch V An Phc Center 5&nbsp;</strong>nm trn trc ng ln TL825 l gii 60m kt ni v cc tnh thnh Hc mn, bnh chnh ,Bnh tn&nbsp; cc qun trung tm ch 25 pht i xe honda cc ng lin khu ti d n u l ng thng nn y c xem l v tr c a thch hp  m qun n nh hng khch sn phc v y  mi khch hng k c khch hng vng lai m bo c thu nhp n nh bn vng hng ngy khi khch hng mua t u t xy dng nh hng khch sn ti d n.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code></code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->', 'KHU  TH  THNG MI  DCH V AN PHC CENTER 5.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '132-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-06-12 16:34:40', '2019-06-12 16:34:40', '', 132, 'http://housing.test/?p=249', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
