(269, 1, '2019-06-12 17:09:38', '2019-06-12 17:09:38', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1191,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":300,\"height\":157,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><a href=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/le_khoi-cong-tuyen-quoc-lo50.jpg?x86971\"><img src=\"http://diaocanphuc.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/le_khoi-cong-tuyen-quoc-lo50-300x157.jpg?x86971\" alt=\"L khi cng d n tuyn quc l 50 n cng Long An\" class=\"wp-image-1191\" width=\"300\" height=\"157\"/></a><figcaption>L khi cng d n tuyn quc l 50 n cng Long An</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NDT  Ngy 3-4, ti Trung tm hc tp cng ng x Tn Tp, huyn Cn Giuc, tnh Long An, UBND tnh Long An  t chc khi cng d n m rng tuyn ng t&nbsp;<a href=\"https://diaocanphuc.com.vn/hon-550-ty-dong-mo-rong-tuyen-quoc-lo-50-den-cang-long-an/\">Quc l 50 n cng Long An.</a>L khi cng&nbsp;<a href=\"https://diaocanphuc.com.vn/category/du-an/\">d n</a>&nbsp;tuyn quc l 50 n cng Long An</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo ngun tin cho bit on t QL50 n Cng Long An c chiu di 12,87 km, vn tc thit k 80&nbsp;km/gi, bo m ti trng 12 tn, mt ng trn nha t cp ba ng bng, nn rng 18,5m, mt ng rng 14m. Tng vn u t hn 550 t ng do ngn sch tnh, vn huy ng doanh nghip v cc ngun vn huy ng hp php khc. Gi thu on t QL50 n Cng Long An s hon thnh trong vng 12 thng k t ngy khi cng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo thng tin c bit, d n on ng t QL50 n Cng Long An l mt hng mc trong D n ng Tn Tp  Long Hu  quc l 50  cng Long An c tng kinh ph u t 1.495 t ng. Trong , ngun vn tri phiu Chnh ph giai on 2017  2020 l 900 t ng, ngn sch tnh v vn huy ng doanh nghip v cc ngun vn huy ng hp php khc l 595 t ng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ring on t quc l 50 n cng Long An, khi hon thnh a vo hot ng s l trc giao thng quan trng phc v nhu cu vn chuyn hng ha t cc khu cng nghip trong tnh n cng Long An v ngc li, gp phn pht trin kinh t x hi ca a phng v cc tnh ln cn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'D n m rng tuyn quc l ti Long An', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'du-an-mo-rong-tuyen-quoc-lo-toi-long-an', '', '', '2019-06-12 17:09:42', '2019-06-12 17:09:42', '', 0, 'http://housing.test/?p=269', 0, 'post', '', 0),
